With an Internet connected computer and some cash, how can you live in a fixed room for three days?
This was a test run 20 years ago -- the first 72 hour online survival competition in China. At that time, "Internet" is still an absolute majority of people unfamiliar with the word, the number of Internet users from the first-tier cities began to grow sporadically. Many people who watched the game all the way realized for the first time that the "Internet" is such a magical existence, straight: "HOW WONDERFUL NETWORK WORLD! "

Time to pull back now, in the face of a sudden epidemic, home quarantine becomes a necessary means of protection, a national Internet survival challenge is being staged.

In the same river of life, the Ministry of Education "suspension without suspension, " the stone thrown, the online education industry waves. Major education platforms such as New Oriental and the monkey guide offer free live online courses and open quality learning resources; Internet giants such as tencent education and Alibaba nail also join the tide head to provide convenient access and technical support, together, they pave the way for an online race track for kids to grow up on, and the 270 million students who attend school are connected to each other through home schooling.

However, "suspension without suspension" does not mean that the online class, the online class is not a simple classroom transfer. In a broad sense, learning is to let children think about the essence of life traces, with the help of the Internet and information-based teaching resources to build their own spiritual sky.

Facing the tablet, the "online" flowers bloom

Facing the tablet, the "online" flowers bloom

"could the college entrance exam be delayed? " Kobayashi, a senior, stared at the countdown on her desk, feeling as uncertain as she was solving a math problem. Unable to go back to school, the school examination also did not fall, she can only review the culture lesson at home.
In fact, whether or not the winter vacation into "staycation" , Kobayashi has already arranged his own vacation review plan, in addition to endorsement brush the problem every day, but also two hours on-air class, special remedial math.
Until the school announces the "opening of the online school" . Kobayashi's schedule was as full as it had been at school, except that it was all online, and she and her classmates began skipping back and forth between classes, clocking in and cutting classes on different platforms, and the "risk" of being asked all of a sudden... the chain of online learning experiences is very different from what she feels when she takes a live class.
The biggest difference is "interaction" . Kobayashi knew that she was not good enough to raise her hand if she had any questions in class, but she felt that she was "more open" during the live class, knowledge is well digested. After-class practice has not understood the place, she also once in the night hurriedly "surprise attack" the teaching assistant teacher, still got the prompt solution.
Using a teaching aid APP from junior high school to a live lesson later, Kobayashi used the internet as a learning aid, a time trajectory that confirms the deep development of China's online education industry.
This winter vacation, Yang mother for the first time to their children Yangyang Choose online courses. After exchanging learning resources with other parents and attending the "parents' class" with the help of Apes, we found that the main teacher could analyze the reasons behind the students' "carelessness" one by one and give out the methods to correct them, that's when Mama Yang made her decision.
Catch up with the new reform of the Beijing high school entrance examination, all junior high school subjects are to be tested, included in the examination results. "Yangyang is now in the second year of junior high school, which is the first year of the exam. The geography and biology exams will be held in June. The time is really quite urgent. " During the epidemic prevention period, the learning environment for online classes was not disturbed by external factors, as a powerful addition to the campus.

To help prepare students for the high school and college entrance exams, the APP launched an online English mock exam for millions of people on February 15, making it the largest number of people online in years. Teaching and learning interact, and exams present the results in the most intuitive form, training children to be more proactive in dissecting their own learning process.

Special working condition

Special working condition

Turning on her computer, Tian turned up the volume to 100 percent, looked for the focus of her face in front of the camera, smiled and said, "hello, class, today we are going to talk about 'My Memories of Old Beijing' and the seeds of kindness. "
As the primary school language teacher, she is in front of the camera every day to start the day's work. After the epidemic hit, APE counseling decided to provide primary and secondary school students across the country free of charge to consolidate learning, through in-depth explanation of subject knowledge to help students consolidate the foundation in class. Therefore, in addition to winter training camp courses, Tian Ying also need to prepare the latest online free live courses.
For the first time at home, Tian Ying surveyed the walls of all the family's rooms in advance and finally came to the conclusion: The Living Room. Class with the table and let Tian Ying launched worry, the height of the table at home are not appropriate. So, she tried to move to the fold-out bed, in the fold-out bed and built a simple storage desk, which built their own "desk. ".

Teacher Tian Ying prepares her lesson at her temporary desk
Unlike in the past, Ms. Tian's class has also become a top priority for her family. When it's time to go to class, she reminds her family to go to the bathroom ahead of time and then hides in their bedrooms. Don't go out, don't make any noise, and don't even use the Internet at home, so as not to interfere with the class during the live broadcast. Such a "domineering" clause was strictly enforced, the family to the Living Room and network to Tian Ying, Tian Ying to thousands of children.
In the "classroom" of ape guidance, you can see all kinds of backdrops: the Big White Wall of the new house you just moved into, the cartoon wallpaper of the heart of a girl, the tiles of the minimalist style... No matter what style, there is always a teacher in front of the camera serious figure, or hard in the lecture, or hunched over a lesson preparation, sometimes busy up for a day to stay.
This attention to the classroom environment is also Liang Liang teacher, where he is located in Huanggang, Hubei, is still the deepest color map of the region.
In order to avoid the students to see the room after the distraction of Sundries, he bought a number of different models of the background plate online, every day a different. In class, with the background close to his back, he had to keep his back straight to prevent any slight wobble in the backboard, and "the angle had to be perfectly adjusted. ".
In addition to lectures, Liang Liang spent most of the time preparing for class, "making courseware" alone, the average class will spend five or six hours. At the end of the day, he usually leaves no more than five hours for sleep.
Suddenly, Liang Liang began to polish the outline of the free class on the third day of the Lunar New Year. He held a meeting with the teachers to discuss and improve the course. Only three days time, they put tens of millions of students need the "spiritual food" ready for the line. Statistics show that five million primary and secondary school students attend the first day of free live ape tutoring classes.
In the past, before each class, Liang Liang teacher will put the study in the two extra doors and windows all closed, reduce noise interference. And in this holiday season, the outdoors is always as quiet as the study. Once again sitting in front of the camera, he can not help but think of the ancient defense of the general, and his guardian is the children's rich learning resources.

Teacher Liang Liang is giving a lesson

Upon Enquiry, Cai learned that Tong's mother's medical team was organizing people to go to Wuhan one after another, she's been working around the clock for days.
Without hesitation, Cai left a message for Tong's mother on Wechat:

Another unwinnable battle, the plague

3

Another unwinnable battle, the plague

For online education, the industry's timeline has been altered by the epidemic.
Previously, online education accounted for less than 10 per cent of the trillion-dollar education and training market. In mid-2019, the forward-looking Industry Research Institute released the "China Online Education Industry Market Outlook and investment strategic planning analysis report, " forecasting that China's online education market will reach 315 billion yuan by 2020. Now, a number of education industry investors have predicted that affected by the epidemic, online education market penetration and market awareness will be greatly improved, the market will be much larger than expected.
In this "network challenge" in the snail house to develop the online learning habits, is gradually embedded into our daily, and precipitation for online education industry inflection point. The gloom is about to lift, and we are all the more grateful for the power of online education: At the most difficult times, it has helped millions of students get their education on track, from a holiday model to a learning state; it has not only explained in detail the knowledge in textbooks, and Broaden Children's horizons with the lessons of Masters.
Some parents in remote areas are putting more emphasis on online education. Shen, who also supports his son's online learning, is based in the county seat of Guangxi, close to Vietnam. As head of the smoking department, he was "on call" for almost 24 hours during the outbreak, not only did he not take a break during the holiday, but he was also in isolation and did not have the time or energy to communicate with Tingting face-to-face. In his view, the use of online education as a way of learning, to break the quarantine brought by the epidemic, but also through the boundaries of geography and imagination. Honed over the lecture notes, the Master's incisive point of view, the infiltration of this knowledge so that the children see the vast stars.

In the face of the epidemic, the enterprise's own ability to cope with the strain is a severe test. Looking back at the starting point of Internet company Alibaba during the SARS period, "during the SARS period, no one should have thought of this as an opportunity, but rather, what kind of trouble we were in and how we could help, " Jack Ma said in a public statement, with the Public Welfare, in this special period for the benefit of every student.
The company donated 10 million yuan to Wuhan to support the urgent needs of front-line medical workers. At the same time, free public welfare courses are open to primary and middle school students nationwide, including the subject consolidation course taught by leading teachers, and the master humanities course taught by top scholars such as JI Lianhai and Montmain, and programming, music and other capacity-building courses, in this "suspension without suspension" of the super-long winter vacation to write down the coordinates of their own.
The war is still going on, but the growing needs of children will not be put on hold. Starting from the epidemic situation itself, mourning, reflection and the light of human nature kindled in the process of fighting the epidemic are precious educational resources. With the full spread of online classes, online education may be embedded in life, constantly inspire the change of learning methods, improve teaching efficiency, will also hit out more sparks of educational content and educational thinking.
